data.about: My name is Shumai born in this beautiful port town  Massawa in native laguage pronounced as 'Mtsi'wa'ea. I have leaved the till I was 3 yeads old and later when I studied. Life then took me to Asmara the capital city and to Nefasit where I spent most of my childhood and teenage years
data.timeline: Born 1984, Achieved diploma in Marine MicroBiology 2008,Achieved Degree in MBT, Fled in 2013
